1) Downlaod samtools and place under this folder
http://samtools.sourceforge.net/
2) build samtools. 
cd samtools
make
cd ..
3) build clustergram
bash make.sh

Simple one step setup
To use samtools samtools-0.1.12a date 01/27/2011, just do
bash make.sh
which automatically download samtools-0.1.12a and continue the compilation
